headline: MetLife Announced as 2025 CIO 100 Award Winner
summary: NEW YORK, March 26, 2025--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) has been named as a 2025 CIO 100 Award Winner by Foundry CIO for My Leave Navigator. For almost 30 years, the CIO 100 Awards have recognized innovative organizations that exemplify the highest level of strategic and operational excellence in IT.
